OL,3,CHow Rachel Reeves learned to love
OL,4,Cbankers
OL,6,FRachel Reeves defended her decision
OL,7,Fnot to restore the cap on bankers'
OL,8,Fbonuses to ITV News' Robert Peston,
OL,9,Finsisting stronger rules are in place
OL,10,Fto prevent risky behaviour in the City
OL,12,FI wanted to explore with the shadow
OL,13,Fchancellor the implications of
OL,14,FLabour's decision to back the
OL,15,Fpermanent removal of the cap on
OL,16,Fbankers' bonuses.
OL,18,FThe best way to do this was to give
OL,19,Fher a concrete example.
