OL,3,CHow Rachel Reeves learned to love
OL,4,Cbankers
OL,6,FReeves was not even slightly
OL,7,Fembarrassed or anxious about my
OL,8,Fquestion. She simply did some mental
OL,9,Farithmetic - and said that on that #2
OL,10,Fmillion bonus she as chancellor, were
OL,11,Fthat to transpire, would pocket
OL,12,F#900,000.
OL,14,FAt a time when our creaking public
OL,15,Fservices desperately need more cash,
OL,16,Fshe'd love a bit of that. What
OL,17,Fchancellor wouldn't want that income-
OL,18,Ftax revenue to fund the salaries of
OL,19,Fabout 20 teachers or 30 nurses?
