OL,3,CHow Rachel Reeves learned to love
OL,4,Cbankers
OL,6,FIt's her variation on Peter
OL,7,FMandelson's feeling of intense
OL,8,Frelaxation about the filthy rich,
OL,9,Fduring the original New Labour era.
OL,11,FBut there is more to this dramatic
OL,12,Frepudiation of Labour's hostility
OL,13,Funder Jeremy Corbyn to the extremes of
OL,14,Fwealth and income inequality than just
OL,15,Fa desire to squeeze every last drop of
OL,16,Ftax out of the economy without
OL,17,Factually putting up taxes.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/7
