OL,3,CHow Rachel Reeves learned to love
OL,4,Cbankers
OL,6,FFirst, Keir Starmer's Labour, like
OL,7,Fthat of Tony Blair and Gordon Brown,
OL,8,Fhas worked out that the UK doesn't
OL,9,Fhave many world-class, high-
OL,10,Fproductivity clusters or industries,
OL,11,Fand financial services is that rarity.
OL,13,FGiven Starmer's "mission" priority to
OL,14,Fstimulate economic growth, it probably
OL,15,Fmakes sense not to hobble the banks
OL,16,Fand the city as his first action if he
OL,17,Fbecomes prime minister.
